# Materials Federation — License File

This repository aggregates data from third-party materials science databases.
All original data remains under the intellectual property and license terms
of its respective source database.

## Data Sources & Their Licenses

### Materials Project
- **License**: [Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 (CC BY 4.0)](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)
- **URL**: https://materialsproject.org
- **Key restriction**: Do not use Materials Project data for training commercial AI/ML models.
- **Attribution**: "Materials Project, https://materialsproject.org"

### JARVIS (NIST)
- **License**: [NIST Terms of Service](https://www.nist.gov/public affairs/nist-websites-terms-and-conditions)
- **URL**: https://jarvis.nist.gov
- **Key restriction**: NIST data is a federal government product; commercial use is limited.
- **Attribution**: "JARVIS, National Institute of Standards and Technology"

### OQMD (Open Quantum Materials Database)
- **License**: [OQMD License Agreement](https://oqmd.org/static/attachment//oqmd_license.pdf)
- **URL**: https://oqmd.org
- **Key restriction**: Commercial use requires a separate license agreement with OQMD.
- **Attribution**: "Open Quantum Materials Database, http://oqmd.org"

### AFLOW
- **License**: [AFLOW License Agreement](http://aflow.org/license/)
- **URL**: http://aflow.org
- **Key restriction**: Direct mirroring prohibited; commercial use requires a license agreement.
- **Attribution**: "AFLOW, http://aflow.org"

### NOMAD (NOMAD Laboratory)
- **License**: [Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 (CC BY 4.0)](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/) and Database Right
- **URL**: https://nomad-lab.eu
- **Attribution**: "NOMAD, https://nomad-lab.eu"

## This Repository

The aggregation code (scripts/sync.py) and YAML data files in this repository
are provided under the [MIT License](./LICENSE.txt).

However, the aggregated **data content** within each YAML file in `materials/`
is sourced from the third-party databases listed above and is subject to their
respective licenses. The license header at the top of each data file identifies
which database(s) contributed that record.

## Disclaimer

All data in this repository originates from third-party public databases.
The repository maintainers do not claim ownership of any original data.
All data remains the intellectual property of the respective database providers.
This aggregation is for research and educational purposes only.

Before using any data from this repository for commercial applications, research,
or publications, you must verify compliance with the license terms of the
relevant source database(s).
